  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a pixel open world survival craft ARPG. It is not a casual style farming simulator. It needs more actions in combat. The game has a linear progress with free world exploration. It needs 30-40 hours to finish the full game.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Building Base</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/74e7149ea3fd7dfe5be9a24701e036b8.poster.avif?t=1758929780\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/74e7149ea3fd7dfe5be9a24701e036b8.webm?t=1758929780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/74e7149ea3fd7dfe5be9a24701e036b8.mp4?t=1758929780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Farming and Crafting</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/cc6cd427598ae5e8b5417fcaf2e28841.poster.avif?t=1758929780\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/cc6cd427598ae5e8b5417fcaf2e28841.webm?t=1758929780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/cc6cd427598ae5e8b5417fcaf2e28841.mp4?t=1758929780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunting</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/cb5d4562040ea70fecfe02664704383f.poster.avif?t=1758929780\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/cb5d4562040ea70fecfe02664704383f.webm?t=1758929780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/cb5d4562040ea70fecfe02664704383f.mp4?t=1758929780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fighting</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/b6eb83a0812a77c23bd28a875123bb8e.poster.avif?t=1758929780\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/b6eb83a0812a77c23bd28a875123bb8e.webm?t=1758929780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/b6eb83a0812a77c23bd28a875123bb8e.mp4?t=1758929780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Nightmare</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nightmares comes at regular intervals, dark monsters will attack the base, its challenging fights and players must prepare well and use everything to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/aee9f503c7f34178cf4baf72abb9d77b.poster.avif?t=1758929780\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/aee9f503c7f34178cf4baf72abb9d77b.webm?t=1758929780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850110/extras/aee9f503c7f34178cf4